underlying_goal: To design a set of AI agents to assist with academic and technical writing, based on provided style guides and principles.
primary_success: Successfully used the `/spec-interview` skill to guide the user from a collection of ideas and links to a structured, detailed specification for a multi-agent writing assistant system.
brief_summary: The user wanted to create AI agents for writing assistance. Using the `/spec-interview` skill, Claude iteratively questioned the user, synthesized provided links and ideas, and produced a detailed specification for a suite of four specialized agents (clarity, narrative, fact-checking, red-teaming). The final spec was saved to a file.
